Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.mobility.sdk.core.geo.Address
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public abstract class Address
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    A generic address type. Note that due to the many different address standards, and different uses of this class, all of its fields are optional.
